{"tid":992043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被插拍旅遊節目無視禁令失禮港人 吳若希：我認我係港女","createTime":"2019-01-23T00:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T03:35:06.000Z","uid":69893,"like":70,"dislike":1234,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"e13fc3b9578968153c1d67e930ec7513f7238529","tid":992043,"uid":69893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T00:53:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/10MVQm?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F10MVQm%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=roOfpUtotHjLxRc6RQnC5JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=88075abf\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/10MVQm?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/23/085015_2b5abeb885ab261dc39cf48d54b80163.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F23%2F085015_2b5abeb885ab261dc39cf48d54b80163.png&h=380f1e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杜如風、吳若希（Jinny）拍攝賀歲節目，對於Jinny在日本旅遊節目中無視禁令摸限量版行李箱，被網友數爆「港女三宗罪」，身為「日本達人」的杜如風說：「不要摸店家的東西，直接給錢買就行了，買完點摸都得啦！」當Jinny自爆摸過的限量版行李箱價值過百萬港元時，如風即笑說：「咁你有排撈！」<br />\nJinny解釋跟足公司指引拍攝：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我認我是港女，但港女即係咩？<span style=\"color: red;\">我相信在節目上是可以觸摸物品</span>，但私下旅行當然不敢亂摸。</span>」她笑問公司為何不贊助她喪買？大感委屈 ，又自爆不怕碌爆卡，皆因卡數一直由老公代找。<br />\n（攝影：鄧國良）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n娶着個咁嘅老婆真係喊三聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daf95c0788d16f5aec1522915731b841c6cd5ae","tid":992043,"uid":67655,"like":786,"dislike":1,"score":785,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T00:57:10.000Z","msg":"知錯唔認<br />\n仲要大大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fab9cc1a7b5e92909489037ba5b4ce7e169ed39","tid":992043,"uid":63859,"like":520,"dislike":5,"score":515,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9949Hc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9949Hc.png&h=48de950d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"807054d61c4598e5af6aaf4923aa3c35a5237f71","tid":992043,"uid":74778,"like":395,"dislike":1,"score":394,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"佢係咪問<strong>我做錯d乜？我唔明囉</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d422ac572f324f790e9f5415a5d66df7948f48d","tid":992043,"uid":95520,"like":623,"dislike":4,"score":619,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:06:04.000Z","msg":"我認我是港女，但港女即係咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你即係認咗啲乜?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信在節目上是可以觸摸物品，但私下旅行當然不敢亂摸。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大撚晒?有咩令你覺得揸住部攝錄機你就特別過普通人?<br />\n<br />\n智將若希又贏"},{"pid":"0a1a68c3d1239448bba2206e1cb034407dfca806","tid":992043,"uid":47210,"like":239,"dislike":1,"score":238,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:06:35.000Z","msg":"屌, 真係以為自己係咩megastar, 拍個濕鳩旅遊節目就大撚曬, 乜都做得咁, 收皮喇好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c66a748e89c5551af6ded535f47733facfe46c","tid":992043,"uid":108266,"like":251,"dislike":1,"score":250,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:11:26.000Z","msg":"連港女都影衰埋就真"},{"pid":"fa0127ec2b1c653133db508c8f67ace1e1a91f80","tid":992043,"uid":76470,"like":81,"dislike":14,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:12:03.000Z","msg":"女權閪又有無野講啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家比條臭雞標籤港女=任性喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快啲出黎屌鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324fb672b950850edbe82054ef4de48484588458","tid":992